title: Grateful Dead Live at Oakland-Alameda County Coliseum on 1991-10-27
lineage: Dat Master (Sony PCM-R500) > Sound Devices 744T > Samplitude Pro X3 Suite > FLAC
description:
Set 1

Sugar Magnolia-> Sugaree, Walkin' Blues, Althea, When I Paint My Masterpiece, Candyman, Cassidy, Touch Of Grey

Set 2

China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Samson & Delilah, Ship of Fools, Iko Iko*-> Mona*-> Jam*-> Drums-> Jam-> The Wheel-> I Need A Miracle-> Wharf Rat-> Good Lovin', E: Knockin' On Heaven's Door

*w/ Carlos Santana & Gary Duncan Quicksilver, guitars; Last "Mona": 03-25-72; Final GD Perfomance of "Mona"

reviews.review_text: the yin & the yang how sweet this is.
10/27 = One of the best of the '91 tour beautiful stuff
